```

So, `|f y - f x| ≤ ∫₀¹ |g' t| dt`.
Now we need to bound `|g' t|`.

```tactics
  have h4 : ∫ (t : ℝ) in (0 : ℝ)..1, |g' t| ≤ ∫ (t : ℝ) in (0 : ℝ)..1, (∑ i : Fin n, |y i - x i| * |nth_partial i f (g₀ t)|) := by
    apply intervalIntegral.integral_le_integral
    intro t ht
